data.description: Come check out this 1,638 SQFT 4Bed/2Bath/2 Car Garage with plenty of living space & tile throughout. Located in the desirable Villa Cordova Sub, & within walking distance to Gowan Science Academy, HLS and Cibola High School. Oh & not to mention this home Features a spacious covered patio and backyard perfect for entertaining, with minimal yard maintenance & citrus trees! Seller is motivated & is offering $5k in buyer concessions.   OPEN HOUSE   SAT 11/18  2PM to 4PM
